com.camerontec.catalys.server.marketdata.service

Class MarketDataServiceBase

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.camerontec.catalys.util.configuration.AbstractConfigurable
      • com.camerontec.catalys.server.component.ComponentHelper
        • com.camerontec.catalys.server.marketdata.service.MarketDataServiceBase
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IComponent, IHasAttributes, IConfigurable, IRegisterable, IMarketDataService, ISubscriptionListener, IService
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DummyMarketDataService, InternalMarketDataService, SampleAggregatedMarketDataService, SampleDerivedPriceMarketDataService, SampleMarketDataService

    public abstract class MarketDataServiceBase
extends ComponentHelper
implements IMarketDataService
    Base implementation of an IMarketDataService which could be a useful base class for creating specific market data services.

    This base implementation automatically:

    • Creates a StandardMarketDataStore, exposed through the standard getMarketDataStore() method.
    • Creates a FixFieldInfos, exposed through the standard getFieldInfos() method. You can use setFieldInfos(com.camerontec.catalys.util.marketdata.IFieldInfos) method to change this default.
    • Supports nested NonStandardData configuration element.
    • Defaults to service name IMarketDataService.DEFAULT_MARKET_DATA_SERVICE_NAME. You can use setServiceName(java.lang.String) method to change this default.
    Note that most ISubscriptionListener methods are missing here and must be implemented in subclasses. This base class automatically registers itself as a subscription listener with its StandardMarketDataStore (by calling addSubscriptionListener).
